    <p>The full client is no longer recommeneded by bitocin.org for most users. &nbsp;They recommend Multibit.org client. &nbsp;That being said, if you do use the full-block chain client, it is much faster to download the bootstrap blockchain over torrent first:&nbsp;<a href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=145386.0" rel="nofollow">https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=145386.0</a></p>

