<p>&nbsp;And ofcourse bitcoin is the ultimate FIAT currency. Contrary to normal FIAT money, which is at least covered by the capability of the state to collect taxes, BTC is covered by absolutely nothing. And it is nothing else than the solution of an equation and there are almost unlimited numbers of equations possible, to create an unlimited amount of Bitcoins (BTC2.0, BTC3.0,...).</p>
<p>This was the first try of the globalists how many sheeple are willing to accept a totally controlled virtual currency. And you have passed the test - they only need to attach a few words to it, like "mining" for solving a equation, or "coin" for a currency unit, and promote it with one of the most stupid lies, that the web was free, anonymous and independent, and enough sheeple from the gold community will bite the bait.</p>
<p>Congratulations! You are freely using a total control globalist currency and you don't even recognize it.</p>

